1、安装PCRE包
 $ sudo apt-get install libpcre3 libpcre3-dev
 $ sudo apt-get install openssl libssl-dev
2、解压:
 $ sudo tar -zxvf /home/jarvis/software/nginx-1.4.7.tar.gz -C /export/server/nginx
3、配置:
 $ sudo cd //export/server/nginx/nginx-1.4.7
 $ sudo ./configure
 $ sudo make
 $ sudo make install
4、安装好的在/usr/local/nginx目录下,进入目录测试
 $ cd /usr/local/nginx
 $ sudo sbin/nginx
5、访问localhost即可看到提示页面
